N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 200.21 - Procedure in local criminal courts; local court rules

State Regulations

Procedure in each local criminal court shall
be as provided by the Criminal Procedure Law and such local court rules as may
be adopted in compliance with Part 9 of the Rules of the Chief Judge (22 NYCRR
Part
9
